original_title: Young woman drowns, another missing in Kirinda
original_body_lines: A woman drowned and another was reported missing after they were carried away by a wave while enjoying a stroll along the beach at Kirinda, Police said.
The body of one of the missing women was recovered this afternoon.
The victims, Sandani Dhananjaya Rajapakse from Welipottayaya in Bibila and Probodhika Kaushanlaya from Seenigoda in Bibila were about 18 years of age and the former was married.
They had gone on a picnic to Kirinda with several other relatives.
Police had launched a search for the other disappeared woman. (Dileep Jayasekara)
